1.0.name: wordpress/swipe-hq-checkout-for-eshop
1.0.description:
This is the Swipe HQ payment gateway for Eshop. Allows you to use SwipeHQ payment gateway with the Eshop plugin. It uses the redirect method, the user is redirected to swipehq so that you don't have to install an SSL certificate on your site. IMPORTANT NOTICE: We recommend that all merchants should update to this plugin version as older versions will no longer be supported.

Visit [http://www.swipehq.com]
